# GoalifyNow E2E (Playwright)

When editing files under `e2e/`, follow:

- `00 - E2E Testing.mdc`
- `00 - E2E Testing - Playwright.mdc`
- `00 - E2E Testing - Best Practices.mdc`

Keep tests aligned with the Angular app in `apps/webapp` and any configured base URL in `e2e/playwright.config.ts`.
